[SHORT DESC]
Increases chances of successfully escaping a random battle.
[LONG DESC]
<p>If this Pok√©mon is in battle, they will be guaranteed the ability to flee so long as they aren't under the effects of full-trapping moves or abilities. This does not apply to trainer battles, where fleeing cannot occur. This does not allow escape from the trapping abilities Shadow Tag or Arena Trap, or the moves Mean Look and Spider Web.</p>